Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:13.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,吃点阿斯匹林,\N早上给我电话.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了, 医生.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt much, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伤的很厉害吗, 宝贝?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, Nadine,\NI was so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝, 纳丁,\N我刚才好担心你啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit there were times\Nwhen I had my doubts
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:27.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我承认我有时\N也会怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about what we meant to each other,\Nbut seeing that sandbag hit you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:33.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们彼此之间到底意味着什么,\N但看着那个沙袋砸到你那一刻,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just knew
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd practicaIIy do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我简直愿意为你做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the tree hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之后那棵树就砸到我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Iove you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, I've said it and I'm gIad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:57.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 我很高兴我说出来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:08.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,迈克.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You try to--\NYou say your name is Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:18.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟想--\N你说你叫迈克?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在我家里干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought me here, Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你带我来这儿的, 纳丁.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能, 你快滚出这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, make him go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德, 快把他赶出去.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing here?
