Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这不公平.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PIease...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, make...
