Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are my drape runners?\NWhere are my drape runners?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:03.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的滑轨窗帘去哪儿了?\N我的滑轨窗帘去哪儿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadine, how oId are you?
