Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me. How oId are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我. 你几岁了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-five, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:15.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,35, 你白痴啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:26.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起, 艾德.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I Iet things\Nget a IittIe out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:31.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是我\N把事情搞糟了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 不要. 不要.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, pIease.\NDonna, pIease Iisten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 求你了.\N唐娜, 请听我说.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I've heard enough.\N- PIease, just Iet me expIain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我已经听够了.\N- 求你了, 让我解释.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Donna...\N- Leave me aIone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 唐娜...\N- 别烦我!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't your parents' fauIt. It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:05.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你父母的错. 都是我害的.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents?\NWho are my parents anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:08.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我父母?\N我父母到底是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I onIy wanted to do good.\NI wanted to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:14.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过想做好事.\N想做个好人.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it feIt so good to teII the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:19.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,时隔多年，终于说出了真相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after aII these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:23.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉真好.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本, 你真该死.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- WiII.\N- Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:35.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 伟.\N- 唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, I warned you.\NGet out of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本, 我警告你.\N滚出我的房子.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WiII,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:41.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伟,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can you forgive me\Nfor what I have done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:47.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能原谅\N我所对你做过的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SyIvia, I toId you to stay home.
