Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 伟. 伟!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WiII!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伟!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I'd seen it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道在哪儿见过它.
