Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'II never notice the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:14:00.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会注意到区别的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Andrew.
